Kornelia Kashiimbindjola Shilunga (amụrụ 25 Mee 1970, Okadila, Oshana Region) bụ onye ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị Namibia na onye otu ọgbakọ omebe iwu kemgbe 2015, [] ọ na-eje ozi ugbu a dị ka osote onye isi ala na-egwupụta akụ na mmanụ

Shilunga nwere nzere masta abụọ, otu na Business Administration na Eastern Southern Africa Management Institute (ESAMI), na nzere nke ọzọ na Public Policy and Administration na Mahadum Namibia (UNAM), nzere bachelọ na Nọọsụ Education na Health Community na Diploma
na Nọọsụ Sayensị General, Community Psychiatry na Midwifery Sciences, sikwa na Mahadum Namibia wee gụọ akwụkwọ na Gabriel Taapopi Senior Secondary School na Ongwediva na 1989.
